001package io.github.ai4ci;
002
003import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
004import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
005import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
006import java.lang.annotation.Target;
007
008import org.immutables.value.Value;
009import org.immutables.value.Value.Style.ValidationMethod;
010
011import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonDeserialize;
012import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonSerialize;
013// import com.j256.simplecsv.common.CsvColumn;
014import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonSerialize.Typing;
015
016import io.github.ai4ci.config.Scale;
017import io.github.ai4ci.flow.output.Export;
018
019/**
020 * Central annotation for configuring Immutables value types with consistent
021 * styling and Jackson serialization support across the codebase.
022 *
023 * <p>
024 * This annotation and its nested styles provide standardized configurations for
025 * Immutables-generated value types, ensuring consistency in:
026 * <ul>
027 * <li>Accessor method naming patterns</li>
028 * <li>Builder initialization patterns</li>
029 * <li>Jackson serialization/deserialization behavior</li>
030 * <li>Hash code, equals, and toString implementations</li>
031 * <li>Pluralization handling for collection properties</li>
032 * </ul>
033 *
034 * <h2>Usage Examples</h2>
035 *
036 * <pre>
037 * {@code @Data.Style}
038 * public interface Person {
039 *     String getName();
040 *     int getAge();
041 * }
042 * </pre>
043 *
044 * <p>
045 * Each nested annotation provides specialized styling for different use cases
046 * while maintaining overall consistency across the codebase.
047 *
048 * @see Value.Style
049 * @see JsonSerialize
050 * @see JsonDeserialize
051 */
052public @interface Data {
053
054        /**
055         * Mutable value type style for modifiable data structures.
056         *
057         * <p>
058         * This style configures types that support mutation with:
059         * <ul>
060         * <li>Standard getter patterns: {@code is*} for booleans, {@code get*} for
061         * others</li>
062         * <li>Builder initialization with {@code set*} methods</li>
063         * <li>Constructor creation with {@code new} instead of builder</li>
064         * <li>Deep immutables detection for nested immutable types</li>
065         * <li>{@code with*} methods for creating modified copies</li>
066         * <li>Automatic toBuilder() implementation</li>
067         * <li>Custom hashCode, equals, and toString underrides</li>
068         * <li>Pluralization support with custom dictionary</li>
069         * </ul>
070         *
071         * <p>
072         * <b>Target Usage:</b> Mutable data structures and configuration objects
073         * where immutability is not required.
074         */
075        @Target({ ElementType.PACKAGE, ElementType.TYPE })
076        @Retention(RetentionPolicy.CLASS)
077        @JsonSerialize(typing = Typing.DYNAMIC)
078        @JsonDeserialize
079        @Value.Style(
080                        get = { "is*", "get*" },
081                        init = "set*",
082                        create = "new",
083                        deepImmutablesDetection = true,
084                        with = "with*",
085                        toBuilder = "toBuilder",
086                        strictBuilder = false,
087                        strictModifiable = false,
088                        underrideHashCode = "hash",
089                        underrideEquals = "equality",
090                        underrideToString = "print",
091                        isSet = "initialised*",
092                        depluralize = true,
093                        depluralizeDictionary = { "person:people" }
094        )
095        public static @interface Mutable {}
096
097        /**
098         * Partial value type style for configuration modifications and patches.
099         *
100         * <p>
101         * This style configures partial types used for:
102         * <ul>
103         * <li>Configuration modifications and overrides</li>
104         * <li>Partial object updates and patches</li>
105         * <li>Demographic adjustment scaling operations</li>
106         * </ul>
107         *
108         * <p>
109         * Key characteristics:
110         * <ul>
111         * <li>Standard getter patterns</li>
112         * <li>Builder initialization with {@code set*} methods</li>
113         * <li>No deep immutables detection (performance optimization)</li>
114         * <li>DemographicAdjustment.Scale annotation pass-through</li>
115         * <li>Type naming pattern: {@code _Partial*} for abstract, {@code Partial*}
116         * for immutable</li>
117         * <li>Custom hashCode, equals, and toString underrides</li>
118         * <li>Pluralization support with custom dictionary</li>
119         * <li>Validation disabled for partial objects</li>
120         * </ul>
121         *
122         * <p>
123         * <b>Target Usage:</b> Configuration patches, demographic adjustments, and
124         * partial object updates.
125         *
126         * @see Scale
127         */
128        @Target({ ElementType.PACKAGE, ElementType.TYPE })
129        @Retention(RetentionPolicy.CLASS)
130        @JsonSerialize(typing = Typing.DYNAMIC)
131        @JsonDeserialize
132        @Value.Style(
133                        get = { "is*", "get*" },
134                        init = "set*",
135                        deepImmutablesDetection = false,
136                        passAnnotations = { Scale.class },
137                        typeAbstract = "_Partial*",
138                        typeImmutable = "Partial*",
139                        strictModifiable = false,
140                        depluralize = true,
141                        underrideHashCode = "hash",
142                        underrideEquals = "equality",
143                        underrideToString = "print",
144                        depluralizeDictionary = { "person:people" },
145                        validationMethod = ValidationMethod.NONE
146        )
147        @SuppressWarnings("immutables")
148        public static @interface Partial {}
149
150        /**
151         * Repository-style configuration for data access objects and persistence
152         * entities.
153         *
154         * <p>
155         * This style optimizes types for repository and data access patterns with:
156         * <ul>
157         * <li>Standard getter patterns</li>
158         * <li>Builder initialization with {@code set*} methods</li>
159         * <li>{@code with*} methods for creating modified copies</li>
160         * <li>Automatic toBuilder() implementation</li>
161         * <li>Custom hashCode, equals, and toString underrides</li>
162         * <li>Export and Import annotation pass-through</li>
163         * <li>Pluralization support with custom dictionary</li>
164         * <li>Initialization state tracking with {@code initialised*} methods</li>
165         * </ul>
166         *
167         * <p>
168         * <b>Target Usage:</b> Data access objects, repository entities, and
169         * persistence-layer models requiring export/import capabilities.
170         *
171         * @see Export
172         * @see Import
173         */
174        @Target({ ElementType.PACKAGE, ElementType.TYPE })
175        @Retention(RetentionPolicy.CLASS)
176        @JsonSerialize(typing = Typing.DYNAMIC)
177        @JsonDeserialize
178        @Value.Style(
179                        get = { "is*", "get*" },
180                        init = "set*",
181                        deepImmutablesDetection = false,
182                        with = "with*",
183                        toBuilder = "toBuilder",
184                        strictBuilder = false,
185                        underrideHashCode = "hash",
186                        underrideEquals = "equality",
187                        underrideToString = "print",
188                        strictModifiable = false,
189                        passAnnotations = { Export.class, Import.class },
190                        isSet = "initialised*",
191                        depluralize = true,
192                        depluralizeDictionary = { "person:people" }
193        )
194        @SuppressWarnings("immutables:from")
195        public static @interface Repository {}
196
197        /**
198         * Standard immutable value type style with full Immutables feature support.
199         *
200         * <p>
201         * This style configures immutable types with:
202         * <ul>
203         * <li>Standard getter patterns: {@code is*} for booleans, {@code get*} for
204         * others</li>
205         * <li>Builder initialization with {@code set*} methods</li>
206         * <li>Deep immutables detection for nested immutable types</li>
207         * <li>{@code with*} methods for creating modified copies</li>
208         * <li>Automatic toBuilder() implementation</li>
209         * <li>Custom hashCode, equals, and toString underrides</li>
210         * <li>Pluralization support with custom dictionary</li>
211         * <li>Export and Import annotation pass-through</li>
212         * </ul>
213         *
214         * <p>
215         * <b>Target Usage:</b> General-purpose immutable data transfer objects and
216         * domain models requiring full Immutables feature set.
217         *
218         * @see Export
219         * @see Import
220         */
221        @Target({ ElementType.PACKAGE, ElementType.TYPE })
222        @Retention(RetentionPolicy.CLASS)
223        @JsonSerialize(typing = Typing.DYNAMIC)
224        @JsonDeserialize
225        @SuppressWarnings("immutables:from")
226        @Value.Style(
227                        // Detect 'get' and 'is' prefixes in accessor methods
228                        get = { "is*", "get*" },
229                        // Builder initialization methods will have 'set' prefix
230                        init = "set*",
231                        deepImmutablesDetection = true,
232                        with = "with*",
233                        toBuilder = "toBuilder",
234                        strictBuilder = false,
235                        underrideHashCode = "hash",
236                        underrideEquals = "equality",
237                        underrideToString = "print",
238                        strictModifiable = false,
239                        passAnnotations = { Export.class, Import.class },
240                        isSet = "initialised*",
241                        depluralize = true,
242                        depluralizeDictionary = { "person:people" }
243        )
244        public static @interface Style {}
245
246}
